    },
    "version_b": {
        "text": "Payment for services rendered will be made within 30 days of invoice receipt.",
        "timestamp": "2023-10-05T14:30:00Z"
    },
    "diff": [
        {"type": "delete", "start_index": 67, "end_index": 71},
        {"type": "insert", "index": 67, "text": "30"}
    ],
    "playbook_rule_id": "rule_001",
    "risk_level": "MEDIUM"
}
```

### 3. **Database Schema**
